item.description:
@ill_pk_ur_as wrote:

ok now you need to go to no-ip.org (do this only if u dont know wat ur ip is) and click “no-ip FREE” now click sign up and do what it tells you after that confirm the the confirmation thing sent to ur email now all u have to do is log in after that check were it sais “current IP” now get those numbers on the server ip of ur moparscape client now go to ur source and click runserver.bat if it has one ok thats all o ya when u click runserver a prompt should popup and it should say “starting (what ever it sais)
server on 0.0.0.0:(port number)” ok if ur port does not say 43594 then change it to what it sais ok ive done all i can.
reply 100% on me!! lol
